snippet.title: Clear Vision 1 Flash Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Clear Vision is a multi part flash game series where you play as a hitman named Jake. He's an ex-military stickman haunted by his nemesis who murdered his family.  The number one thing he longs for is revenge!

There's many different levels where you have to read into the details to find the right target.  There's also usually a lot of funny bits in the newspaper.  Make sure you try the new product "Change!"
